{"tid":954941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫檢師偷吃嫩學妹　婆婆作證：他登門送九層塔","createTime":"2018-12-25T04:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T05:51:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"81e5744160b4e659698d759af5de50d11d8cacf5","tid":954941,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"醫檢師間發生外遇，男女相差20歲，女方婆婆從媳婦手機看到鹹溼訊息，又撞見2人運動，甚至對方還帶九層塔上門，才知兒子被戴綠帽。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，北部某醫院女醫檢師外遇大她20歲的張姓學長，2人訊息露骨，人妻對張說，「老色鬼，超想您的」，張姓醫檢師也回覆「您不是說您是正常女人。您不是喜歡做嗎？」、「孩子吃墮胎藥即可。其實也不需怎麼拿掉，我們愛愛用力撞擊就掉了。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女方婆婆看到媳婦簡訊，還撞見2人一起晨間運動。婆婆作證時說，發現媳婦的手機有曖昧簡訊，媳婦卻兇說「這個家我早就不想要了」；張姓男子還曾登門送九層塔。高院認為，2人往來逾分際，女醫檢師的丈夫其配偶權不能被侵犯，判賠40萬元。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/SecondhandLavishGreatargus-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FSecondhandLavishGreatargus-size_restricted.gif&h=daa7d820&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86a40f3e2ecb95cdfc35ce8fd7eaacf80561e892","tid":954941,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"我們愛愛用力撞擊就掉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d4c2b041ebd4f57a901144ee99522bafd408c1","tid":954941,"uid":130280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"新北？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4553232a32b8a266098a6d34366cce0622aa6232","tid":954941,"uid":62990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"台灣潮文！唔該。"},{"pid":"e9768780d2a7a8f86f517fdd37df1fa761013bde","tid":954941,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4553232a32b8a266098a6d34366cce0622aa6232","tid":954941,"uid":62990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"台灣潮文！唔該。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:52:43.000Z","msg":"所"},{"pid":"24981e2e99b17e2e78254bb31ca81e89662f7726","tid":954941,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"所...."},{"pid":"e196172859dcd74976c078008f4c7fd23af1acb8","tid":954941,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"九層塔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}